Kagayaita no ha
What shined was

145
00:10:11,860 --> 00:10:17,343
Kagami demo taiyou demo nakute
Neither the mirror nor the sun

146
00:10:17,343 --> 00:10:23,423
Kimi dato kiduita toki kara
But you. Since then

147
00:10:23,423 --> 00:10:27,282
Ano namidagumu kumo no zutto
