Love story mata hitotsu
Another love story

150
00:10:37,629 --> 00:10:44,600
Kidutuita yume ha kinou no kanata he
Take the wounded dreams to yesterday

151
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:52,466
Sora ni hibike ai no uta
The sky will echo with the song of love

152
00:10:54,001 --> 00:10:58,719
Omoide zutto zutto wasurenai sora
The sky will always, always remember the memories

153
00:10:58,719 --> 00:11:02,067
Futari ga hanarete itemo
No matter if we are separated

154
00:11:02,067 --> 00:11:04,849
Konna sukina hito ni
For the girl I love so much

155
00:11:04,849 --> 00:11:08,673
Deau kisetsu nido to nai
Even if we won't meet the second time

156
00:11:08,673 --> 00:11:12,404
Hikatte motto saokou no lady
Shine more, you're the best lady

157
00:11:12,404 --> 00:11:15,850
Kitto sotto omoi todoku
My feelings will definitely, gently reach to you

